fulltitle: Teo Macero on Working with Dave Brubeck and Miles Davis
description: In this clip from www.artistshousemusic.org - Producer and arranger Teo Macero discusses working with musicians Dave Brubeck and Miles Davis.
title: Teo Macero on Working with Dave Brubeck and Miles Davis
